claimJuryFees(uint256).details: v3.7.0: Each winning voter claims their proportional share individually      This replaces the loop in _distributeJuryFees to prevent gas griefing

params.marketId: The market to claim jury fees from

confirmAction(uint256).details: ReplaceSigner requires 2-of-3, all other actions require 3-of-3      Auto-executes when required confirmations reached

params.evidenceLink: URL to source of truth for resolution (can be empty for degen markets)
params.heatLevel: The heat level for market volatility
params.imageUrl: URL to market image/thumbnail (IPFS or HTTP, can be empty)
params.question: The prediction question
params.resolutionRules: Clear rules for how to resolve

createMarketAndBuy(string,string,string,.details: This guarantees the creator is the first buyer - impossible to front-run      msg.value must cover both marketCreationFee + minBet

dispute(uint256).details: Requires 2x the proposal bond. Triggers voting period.      v3.6.1: Removed cutoff check - disputes are always allowed within their 30-min window      The proposal cutoff at 22h ensures resolution always completes before 24h refund      (proposal at 21:59 + 30min dispute + 1h voting = 23:29, well before 24h)

params.marketId: The market with the proposal to dispute

emergencyRefund(uint256).details: Available 24h after expiry if: no proposal, or voting resulted in tie      v3.6.2: Blocked if a proposal exists (must finalize first), unless contract is paused

executeAction(uint256).details: ReplaceSigner requires 2-of-3, all other actions require 3-of-3

finalizeMarket(uint256).details: Can be called by anyone. Distributes bonds to winners.

getMaxSellableShares(uint256,uint256,boo.details: Uses binary search to find max shares where grossBnbOut <= poolBalance

params.isYes: Whether selling YES or NO shares
params.userShares: The user's total shares on this side

returns.bnbOut: Net BNB the user would receive after fees
returns.maxShares: Maximum shares that can be sold without exceeding pool balance

proposeOutcome(uint256,bool).details: Requires bond payment. Creator has priority in first 10 minutes.

params.marketId: The market to propose outcome for
params.outcome: The proposed outcome (true = YES wins, false = NO wins)

params.newBondWinnerShare: New bond winner share in basis points (2000-8000 = 20%-80%)

params.newDynamicBondBps: New dynamic bond in basis points (50-500 = 0.5%-5%)

proposeSetFee(uint8,uint256).details: Platform: max 500 (5%), Creator: max 200 (2%), Resolution: max 100 (1%), MarketCreation: max 0.1 BNB

params.feeType: The type of fee to set (Platform=0, Creator=1, Resolution=2, MarketCreation=3)
params.newValue: The new fee value (BPS for Platform/Creator/Resolution, wei for MarketCreation)

params.level: The heat level to set (CRACK=0, HIGH=1, PRO=2, APEX=3, CORE=4)

params.newProposerReward: New proposer reward in basis points (max 200 = 2%)

vote(uint256,bool).details: Vote weight equals total shares owned. Free to vote.

params.outcome: The outcome to vote for (true = YES, false = NO)
